## The Challenge

A growing SaaS company needed to consolidate data from multiple sources into a single source of truth, with real-time visibility into pipeline health.

## Our Solution

We designed and built:

- **ETL pipelines** pulling from 8 different data sources
- **Real-time dashboard** showing pipeline status, data quality metrics, and alerts
- **Automated data validation** catching issues before they reach the warehouse
- **Self-healing mechanisms** that automatically retry failed jobs

## The Results

- **100%** data source coverage (up from 60% manual)
- **Real-time** visibility into data health
- **Zero** missed data loads since deployment
- Engineering team reclaimed **15 hours/week** previously spent on manual data tasks
